/**
 * default-data.js
 * Built-in example dataset and pre-filled model strings for FANGS.
 *
 * The CSV matches data/example.csv, generated by tests/r-reference/generate-default-data.R
 * with set.seed(42):
 *   y_i = 2 + 1.5*x_i + b_{group[i]} + eps_i
 *   b_group ~ N(0, sigma_b^2), sigma_b = 0.5
 *   eps_i   ~ N(0, sigma^2),   sigma   = 0.7
 * N=50, 5 groups (10 obs each).
 *
 * OLS sanity check: alpha ≈ 2.29, beta ≈ 1.38 (close to true values after
 * accounting for absorbed group effects in the simple linear model).
 */

